{"tid":2304187,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"【廢佬】確診余錦基周日曾到太古城Audi陳列室除罩","createTime":"2020-11-28T14:13:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T14:45:24.000Z","uid":275570,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aa8725f1353fa61ed976de3f6514d8c4aae593ec","tid":2304187,"uid":275570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T14:13:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201128/76E2Q6QHTNA23KTJRHFZEVQ3GE/?utm_source=whatsapp&amp;utm_medium=messenger&amp;utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_content=share_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201128%2F76E2Q6QHTNA23KTJRHFZEVQ3GE%2F%3Futm_source%3Dwhatsapp%26utm_medium%3Dmessenger%26utm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoRxQ2JDI1%2B2PXXyGzAukhOpM%3D&h=30b9386c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201128%2F76E2Q6QHTNA23KTJRHFZEVQ3GE%2F%3Futm_source%3Dwhatsapp%26utm_medium%3Dmessenger%26utm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&h=0a1ba9fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201128/76E2Q6QHTNA23KTJRHFZEVQ3GE/?utm_source=whatsapp&amp;utm_medium=messenger&amp;utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_content=share_link</a><br />\n<br />\n確診余錦基周日曾到太古城Audi陳列室 除罩睇澳門賽車直播<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》接獲爆料指，確診武漢肺炎、正留醫屯門醫院的汽車會會監余錦基，於周日（22日）曾到位於太古城Audi的旗艦陳列室，與一班朋友睇澳門賽車的賽事直播，其間一度除下口罩，飲咖啡及與友人傾計，包括Audi高層。爆料人事後指該公司未有即時消毒。<br />\n<br />\nAudi發言人接受《蘋果》查詢時承認余該日曾到訪陳列室，公司其後得知余確診之後，已安排專業人士為陳列室進行消毒及清潔。強調余錦基當日沒有睇車，而前線職員也沒有與他有密切接觸，但部份職員為安全起見，已自行進行病毒檢測，暫未有其他人士確診。<br />\n<br />\n至於當日與余同場人士中，有多少人要送往檢疫及進行病毒檢測，《蘋果》正向衞生署查詢。"},{"pid":"f55c8c39ddd22af81a3829d288be28ca5b14309b","tid":2304187,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T14:45:24.000Z","msg":"錦龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}